Class Authorisation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.team2.cluk.backend.webresources.Authorisation
  • @Path("/")
public class Authorisation
extends java.lang.Object
    Authorisation class which handles accounts within the database It enables account permissions for Restaurant, Warehouse and Driver
